<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jarvis - Control de Disponibilidad Docente</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #0052cc; /* Color azul del proyecto */
            --light-blue: #deebff;
            --danger-red: #d93025;
            --bg-gray: #f4f5f7;
            --text-dark: #172b4d;
            --border-color: #dee2e6;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-gray);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(9, 30, 66, 0.08);
        }

        header {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bg-gray);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #5e6c84;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .stats-badge {
            background-color: var(--light-blue);
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .search-box {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .search-box input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .search-box input:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--light-blue);
        }

        .suggestions {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            max-height: 250px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(9,30,66,0.15);
            display: none;
        }

        .suggestions div {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f4f5f7;
        }

        .suggestions div:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .suggestions div:hover {
            background-color: var(--light-blue);
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .schedule-card {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .teacher-info {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #091e42;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: white;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f4f5f7;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #5e6c84;
            width: 14%;
        }

        th:first-child {
            width: 16%;
        }

        .time-col {
            font-weight: 600;
            background-color: #fafbfc;
            color: #5e6c84;
        }

        /* Bloque de hora Ocupada en Azul */
        .occupied {
            background-color: var(--primary-blue) !important;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.25s ease;
        }

        /* Nota de Docentes Compartidos en Rojo */
        .shared-note {
            display: none;
            background-color: #ffebe6;
            color: var(--danger-red);
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--danger-red);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-2px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <div>
            <h1>Jarvis - Disponibilidad Docente</h1>
            <p>Busca un profesor para ver en qué bloques horarios semanales está dictando clase.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-badge" id="teacherCount">118 Docentes Activos</div>
    </header>

    <!-- Caja de Búsqueda -->
    <div class="search-box">
        <input type="text" id="searchTeacher" placeholder="Escribe el apellido o nombre del docente..." autocomplete="off">
        <div id="suggestions" class="suggestions"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel del Calendario -->
    <div class="schedule-card">
        <div class="teacher-info" id="selectedTeacherName">Selecciona un docente para visualizar su agenda</div>
        
        <table id="scheduleTable">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Hora</th>
                    <th>Lunes</th>
                    <th>Martes</th>
                    <th>Miércoles</th>
                    <th>Jueves</th>
                    <th>Viernes</th>
                    <th>Sábado</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="scheduleBody">
                <!-- Se autogenera dinámicamente -->
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Nota informativa roja de compartidos -->
        <div id="sharedNote" class="shared-note"></div>
    </div>
</div>

